{%- comment -%}
  Vivid — The team / credentials page. Anonymous origin story (user request)
  but credentialed and authoritative for E-E-A-T and GEO.
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="cred-hero">
  <div class="container cred-hero-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">The family behind Vivid</p>
      <h1>Built by an SA family who's been in the apothecary since 1996.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Vivid is the modern face of a family-owned health business that started in 1996 in a small Gauteng home, when a parent searched the country for help for a sick child and couldn't find a single store that explained what was in the bottle. So the family opened their own. Today there are three Onelife Health stores in Gauteng and Vivid — the family's own line, made the way they wished other brands made theirs.</p>
      <p class="lede">We don't put a single founder face on Vivid because it wasn't a single person — it's a family standard, kept anonymous on purpose.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="cred-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Vivid is reviewed by</p>
      <ul class="cred-list">
        <li><strong>An in-house clinical advisor</strong><br>Registered SA naturopath. Available free for any Vivid customer — every quiz result, every order, any time.</li>
        <li><strong>A registered pharmacist</strong><br>Reviews every formulation for drug-interaction safety before launch.</li>
        <li><strong>An ISO 17025-aligned SA lab</strong><br>Independently tests every batch for identity, potency and heavy metals.</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/pages/consultation" class="btn primary">Book a free consultation →</a>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cred-belief">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">What we believe</p>
    <ol class="belief-list">
      <li><strong>Labels should tell the truth.</strong> The exact milligrams of every active. No proprietary blends. No "complex" hiding 5mg of something where you needed 500mg.</li>
      <li><strong>Plants first.</strong> When a botanical does the job, the botanical does the job. We only reach for a synthetic active when the evidence demands it.</li>
      <li><strong>Tested before sold.</strong> Every batch, every release. No batch ships without independent verification.</li>
      <li><strong>Free expert access.</strong> A real human reads your quiz result and replies to your questions. No bot, no upsell script.</li>
      <li><strong>Built in South Africa.</strong> Encapsulated and labelled in Centurion. The 3 Onelife stores stand behind it.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cred-credentials">
  <div class="container cred-credentials-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Credentials</p>
      <h2>Receipts.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="cred-pills">
      <span class="cred-pill">30 years in SA health retail</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">3 physical stores (Gauteng)</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">SAHPRA-aligned formulations</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">ISO 17025-aligned lab testing</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">SA Naturopath-supervised</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">Pharmacist-reviewed</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">POPIA-compliant</span>
      <span class="cred-pill">Made in Centurion</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "AboutPage",
  "name": "The team behind Vivid Health",
  "url": {{ shop.url | append: '/pages/the-team' | json }},
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Vivid Health",
    "foundingDate": "1996",
    "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "addressLocality": "Centurion", "addressRegion": "Gauteng", "addressCountry": "ZA" },
    "sameAs": [
      "https://www.instagram.com/vividhealthsa",
      "https://www.tiktok.com/@vividhealthsa"
    ]
  }
}
</script>

